item.title: About Me
item.description: Hello! I am Md. Zunaed Karim. I am from Dhaka, Bangladesh. Currently I am completing my B.Sc. in Computer Science and Engineering at Bangladesh University of Engineering and Technology. I usually do web development works, with special interest in backend development and DevOps tools. To know more about my works, visit my projects page. In my spare time, I love to read books, watch movies, TV series and travel to places with my friends.
